snippet.title: Pixels Online - Sunshine and Grainbows, Flour Powder Quests - Chapter 1
snippet.description: Here's the guide to unlocking and completing Sunshine and Grainbows and Flour Powder quests. The first quest unlocks once you reach farming level 5, and the second quests immediately starts right after.
